- Collector focus: The album‑oriented presentation and analogue craft appeal to my preference for cohesive albums rather than single‑track mastering.
Why I reject CD 1
- Compilation format: CD 1 is a series‑backed Greatest Hits — that flags the core dislike I listed for compilation/"best‑of" fragmentation and single‑track mastering. Even with “consistent mastering,” the very nature of a hits compilation tends to prioritize track‑level presentation over an album narrative I prize.
